title: Mojave Mo' Problems
description: Patrolling the Mojave almost makes you wish for a nuclear winter. Mojave, Mo' Problems is a hardcore exlcusive list which transforms New Vegas into a survival RPG. Heat, Diseases, and an overhauled combat experience turn the Mojave into an enemy in itself.
author: Camora
